{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847212171,"sessionID":"ses_28742d97fffe2oXNNCTsjNslVt","part":{"id":"prt_d78bd83d4001w5Ym9ksEY3F3ab","messageID":"msg_d78bd783d001UCTx5q3GPTQJaJ","sessionID":"ses_28742d97fffe2oXNNCTsjNslVt","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-f9e94fefed0d41939dd806cdcc974ae7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-008\n- **Title**: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nImplement a scheduled garbage collection mechanism for sandbox resources.\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Related Changes\nNone","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-008/CHANGE.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-008/CHANGE.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-008/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775847212132,"end":1775847212169}}}}
